column2: select Album.Title, Artist.Name as Artist, count(Track.TrackId) as TrackNumbers, sum(Track.UnitPrice) as AlbumPrice from chinook.Album JOIN chinook.Track  ON Track.AlbumId = Album.AlbumId JOIN chinook.Artist  ON Album.ArtistId = Artist.ArtistId GROUP BY Album.Title, Artist.Name ORDER BY AlbumPrice DESC
